channel.title: Modified Ancient Tab?
channel.description:
I'm trying to develop an information tab next to the Friends Tab (Were ancients normally is) I don't have ancients on my side tab and I need to know how I can put text into that tab. Something like:
[code] if (warnLevel >= 0) { sendQuest("@bla@ You have a warn level of @gre@ 0%", ###); }[/code]
I want to know the placement numbers, for example on the Emotes Tab the thing that says emotes and animations is 174.
Can someone post the range for these numbers?
Like: 1-20
Or: 653-673

item.title: Modified Ancient Tab?
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

To make frames in the place of that empty tab, you need to insert a side bar Interface into it. I do not know which interface would fit in there without going ‘out of bounds’. Also, the only interface I know that can do that is either the Music tab or quest tab…
